      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>General record for the miracle of the bishop of Rome who cut off his own hand. This miracle circulates in a long version,
               <ref type="work" corresp="LIT5904MMAbbasLong"/>, beginning with his conversion from Islam as a young man, and a short version,
               <ref type="work" corresp="LIT5903MMAbbasShort"/>, which lacks the conversion story and seems to be condensed overall.</p>
         </abstract>
